77
00:09:19.267 --> 00:09:22.187 line:82%
I'm Samya Siddique. You are?

78
00:09:26.232 --> 00:09:29.819 line:82%
Do you want me to call you 786,
like the others do?

79
00:09:31.154 --> 00:09:35.033 line:82%
I'm sure your name isn't that bad
that you'd like to be known by numbers.

80
00:09:41.748 --> 00:09:43.208 line:82%
Veer Pratap Singh.

81
00:09:48.463 --> 00:09:51.007 line:82%
You're hearing your name
after ages, right?

82
00:09:57.305 --> 00:09:59.307 line:82%
Veer Pratap Singh, please talk to me.

83
00:09:59.307 --> 00:10:01.601 line:82%
I'm here to help you.

84
00:10:03.978 --> 00:10:06.981 line:82%
