211
00:23:23.652 --> 00:23:26.196 line:82%
Come on, drink this holy water now.

212
00:23:27.906 --> 00:23:29.408 line:82%
Grandma.

213
00:23:32.161 --> 00:23:33.579 line:82%
Grandma?

214
00:23:34.997 --> 00:23:37.082 line:82%
Grandma...

215
00:24:03.734 --> 00:24:07.696 line:82%
She was in Pakistan,
and you were in India.

216
00:24:09.448 --> 00:24:11.784 line:82%
