My beloved passes by

411
00:39:47.385 --> 00:39:49.554 line:82%
the one who has fallen in love with her

412
00:39:49.554 --> 00:39:51.931 line:82%
Oh, my beloved!

413
00:39:51.931 --> 00:39:57.228 line:82%
My beloved is amazing,
she chants the name of God

414
