01:34:56.774 --> 01:35:00.111 line:82%
The fates of all of them
were connected to it.

1071
01:35:01.487 --> 01:35:05.033 line:82%
In such a situation,
Zaara leaving for India all by herself

1072
01:35:05.033 --> 01:35:08.119 line:82%
