irresponsible behavior.

1073
01:35:08.119 --> 01:35:10.830 line:82%
And forgiving such behavior

1074
01:35:10.830 --> 01:35:14.709 line:82%
was not what
Jahangir Hayat Khan would do.

1075
01:35:14.709 --> 01:35:18.338 line:82%
It had been a month
since Zaara returned.

1076
01:35:18.338 --> 01:35:22.258 line:82%
But her father hadn't spoken to her.

1077
01:35:22.258 --> 01:35:25.303 line:82%
Oh, my! This is amazing!

1078
01:35:25.303 --> 01:35:27.597 line:82%
